{
  "stem": "1775.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they never-- they were so bloodthirsty that they always killed before they told you what they wanted.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I don't think there's enough written about Meserich.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because there were so many people going through Meserich, coming there, seeking refuge, and getting-- getting refuge, and getting things, as much as people could.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They always tried to help those people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the people didn't-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe there's books and things written about Meserich that I don't know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I know there's one book written about Meserich, but it's written in Hebrew and in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were very much against it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We wanted it to be written in English, too, just because our children, you know, cannot speak Yiddish or something.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The English comes easier to them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they were trying to translate it to English, but it never came about.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One thing that Meserich is doing now is they're trying to build a fence around the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was one cemetery that the Germans just took apart, that was the old cemetery.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then there was the newer cemetery, and they took everything out, all the [INAUDIBLE] and the, you know, headstones, and the things.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They took everything apart.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they made like sidewalks out of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "One of the ladies from Meserich which resided in the United States, her-- her name was Sarah Finkelstein.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Her husband, they gave a large donation to Meserich to begin with to pick up all those stone-- headstones and things.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they made something out of this on the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Now they're trying to build a fence around the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I think the Polish government from Meserich is working with them on it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They hope to have it done.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It's in progress.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my cousin is very active with it.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
